{"type": "article", "id": 3864, "title": "日用榨油机", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-26T07:30:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233047KrjO4Yk6blDPSmsM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t内地层出不穷的地沟油事件今年蔓延到了台湾，为了让更多的人吃上健康放心的油，台湾国立成功大学工业设计系的 3 位毕业生谌志仁、邱柏钧以及吴育欣干脆设计了一款名为「一日油行」（ Daily Expeller )的日用榨油机，来帮助人们塑造健康吃油的生活习惯。这款榨油机可以依用户自己的口味，选择各式菜籽、花生、芝麻、核桃、向日葵等原料，只需简单的炒、碎、蒸与榨 4 个步骤，花费 15 分钟，便可以萃取出足以两人份食用的油。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XNzEzMjQxMzgw\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233044N0qazx64BQjlpgJ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233044GPfea02tzMbrx9kJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330458KC2bqwQsHOpgFMr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233045FREzs0dQi87kJLOp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233046amChYpfGFgzcTQr2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}